      "text": "もう{user}さんとの打ち合わせの時間だ\nうひゃぁぁ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's already time for the meeting with {user}-san.\nOh my gosh!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！？　いつの間に！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!? When did you get here!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんごめん、凄く集中してるから\n話し掛けるタイミングが見つからなくてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ sorry. You seemed really focused‚\nand I couldn't find the right timing to talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうだったんですね\nすみません、つい夢中になっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I see.\nI'm sorry‚ I got carried away…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "そろそろ打ち合わせのお時間ですよね\n始めましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's about time for our meeting‚ isn't it?\nLet's get started!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、さっきはどうしてエントランスにいたんだ？\n仕事の合間の勉強なら、いつもオフィスでしてるだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ why were you at the entrance earlier?\nDon't you usually study in the office during your breaks?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "もうじき定期テストがあって……\nその勉強をしてたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have an upcoming midterm test…\nI was studying for it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか。それにしても……\nさっきみたいに悩んでるのは初めて見たな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. But still…\nIt's the first time I've seen you so troubled like earlier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "……自分で言うのもなんなんですけど\nいつもは結構、手際よく勉強してたつもりなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It might sound strange coming from me‚\nbut I usually study pretty efficiently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.9333433334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "忙しくても時間を見つけて宿題やテスト勉強を\nしてたんですけど……最近はその暇さえなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when I'm busy‚ I find time to do homework and study for tests.\nBut lately‚ I haven't even had time for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "テスト範囲で急に気になるところが思い浮かんで\nそれであの場で教科書を広げて確認してたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suddenly‚ I started worrying about the topics for the test‚\nso I opened my textbook right there to check.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな……今回はかなり焦ってる訳か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… So this time‚ you're quite panicked.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "元々は{user}さんがもう少しお仕事を\nセーブしようとしてくれてましたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Originally‚ {user}-san was trying to save me\nfrom taking on too much work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、興味のあるお仕事がいっぱいあって\n私がどれもこれもやりたいですって言い過ぎて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I got carried away and\nsaid I wanted to do everything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.6000100001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "その結果が今という感じなので、さすがに\nお仕事を受け過ぎちゃったなーって反省してます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And now‚ I'm reflecting on it\nbecause this is the result.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり無理がきてしまったよな……\nすまない、俺がちゃんとセーブするべきだった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You pushed yourself too hard‚ huh…\nI'm sorry‚ I should have done a better job at saving you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ！　私が悪いんですから気にしないで下さい！\nお仕事自体は凄く勉強になってますし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no! It's my fault‚ so please don't worry about it!\nThe work itself is a valuable learning experience!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "……まぁ、初めてのお仕事の準備に気合いを入れて\n勉強時間がなくなっちゃったんですけど……えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ I put a lot of effort into preparing for my first job‚\nso I ended up with no study time… Ehehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんや鈴村さんには相談したのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Have you talked to Tendo-san or Suzumura-san about it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "きっと瑠依ちゃんも優ちゃんも\n協力してくれると思うんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure Rui-chan and Yu-chan\nwould be willing to help‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
